# Input

```svelte
{#await promise then { name, age, address }}
<div>
<p>Name: {name}</p>
<p>Age: {age}</p>
<p>Address: {address}</p>
</div>
{/await}

```


# Formatted

```svelte
{#await promise then { name, age, address }}
	<div>
		<p>Name: {name}</p>
		<p>Age: {age}</p>
		<p>Address: {address}</p>
	</div>
{/await}

```
